msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:108.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āḷavakā bhikkhū navakammaṃ karontā aṭṭakaṃ bandhanti."
msgstr "On one occasion, the monks of Āḷavī, while doing building work, were putting together an elevated platform."

