msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:156.6"
msgid "māresi."
msgstr "and he died."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:156.7"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "The first monk became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:156.8"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, ­namara­ṇādhip­pāyassā”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense for one who is not aiming at death.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:156.9"
msgid "(94)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="151"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.526" href="#ms.526"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āḷavakā bhikkhū navakammaṃ karontā rukkhaṃ chindanti."
msgstr "On one occasion, the monks of Āḷavī, while doing building work, felled a tree."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.2"
msgid "Aññataro bhikkhu maraṇādhippāyo aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "A monk, meaning to kill a second monk, said to him,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.3"
msgid "“āvuso, atraṭṭhito chindāhī”ti."
msgstr "“Fell it while standing here.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.4"
msgid "Taṃ tatraṭṭhitaṃ chindantaṃ"
msgstr "He did."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.5"
msgid "rukkho ottharitvā māresi … pe …"
msgstr "The tree fell on him, and he died. …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.6"
msgid "rukkho ottharitvā na māresi."
msgstr "The tree fell on him, but he did not die."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.7"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "The first monk became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.8"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.9"
msgid "āpatti thullaccayassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s a serious offense.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:157.10"
msgid "(95–‍96)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="152"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.3.5.31" href="#Bu-Pj.3.5.31"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.527" href="#ms.527"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:158.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū dāyaṃ ālimpesuṃ;"
msgstr "On one occasion, monks from the group of six set fire to a forest grove."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:158.2"
msgid "manussā daḍḍhā kālamakaṃsu."
msgstr "Some people were burnt and died."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:158.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "The monks became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:158.4"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhave, ­namara­ṇādhip­pāyassā”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense for one who is not aiming at death.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:158.5"
msgid "(97)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="153"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.528" href="#ms.528"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:159.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū maraṇādhippāyā dāyaṃ ālimpesuṃ."
msgstr "On one occasion, monks from the group of six, meaning to cause death, set fire to a forest grove."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:159.2"
msgid "Manussā daḍḍhā kālamakaṃsu … pe …"
msgstr "Some people were burnt and died. …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:159.3"
msgid "manussā daḍḍhā na kālamakaṃsu."
msgstr "Some people were burnt, but did not die."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:159.4"
msgid "Tesaṃ kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "The monks became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:159.5"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhave, pārājikassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:159.6"
msgid "āpatti thullaccayassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s a serious offense.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:159.7"
msgid "(98–‍99)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="154"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.3.5.32" href="#Bu-Pj.3.5.32"></a><a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.86" href="#Vin.3.86"></a> <a class="ms-pa" id="ms.529" href="#ms.529"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu āghātanaṃ gantvā coraghātaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "On one occasion, a monk went to a place of execution and said to the executioner,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.2"
msgid "“āvuso, māyimaṃ kilamesi."
msgstr "“Donʼt torture him."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.3"
msgid "Ekena pahārena jīvitā voropehī”ti."
msgstr "Kill him with a single blow.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.4"
msgid "“Suṭṭhu, bhante”ti"
msgstr "“All right, Venerable,” he said,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.5"
msgid "ekena pahārena jīvitā voropesi."
msgstr "and he killed him with a single blow."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.6"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "The monk became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.7"
msgid "“āpattiṃ tvaṃ, bhikkhu, āpanno pārājikan”ti."
msgstr "“You have committed an offense entailing expulsion.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:160.8"
msgid "(100)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="155"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.530" href="#ms.530"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu āghātanaṃ gantvā coraghātaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "On one occasion, a monk went to a place of execution and said to the executioner,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.2"
msgid "“āvuso, māyimaṃ kilamesi."
msgstr "“Donʼt torture him."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.3"
msgid "Ekena pahārena jīvitā voropehī”ti."
msgstr "Kill him with a single blow.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.4"
msgid "So—“nāhaṃ tuyhaṃ vacanaṃ karissāmī”ti"
msgstr "“I wonʼt do as you ask,” he said,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.5"
msgid "taṃ jīvitā voropesi."
msgstr "and he executed him."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.6"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "The monk became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.7"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.8"
msgid "āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s an offense of wrong conduct.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:161.9"
msgid "(101)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="156"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.3.5.33" href="#Bu-Pj.3.5.33"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.531" href="#ms.531"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro puriso ñātighare ­hattha­pādac­chinno ñātakehi samparikiṇṇo hoti."
msgstr "On one occasion, a man whose hands and feet had been cut off was in his relatives’ house surrounded by his relations."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.2"
msgid "Aññataro bhikkhu te manusse etadavoca—"
msgstr "A monk said to those people,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.3"
msgid "“āvuso, icchatha imassa maraṇan”ti?"
msgstr "“Would you like him to die?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.4"
msgid "“Āma, bhante, icchāmā”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, Venerable.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.5"
msgid "“Tena hi takkaṃ pāyethā”ti."
msgstr "“Then you should give him buttermilk.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.6"
msgid "Te taṃ takkaṃ pāyesuṃ."
msgstr "They gave him buttermilk"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.7"
msgid "So kālamakāsi."
msgstr "and he died."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.8"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "The monk became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.9"
msgid "“āpattiṃ tvaṃ, bhikkhu, āpanno pārājikan”ti."
msgstr "“You have committed an offense entailing expulsion.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:162.10"
msgid "(102)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><div class="bhikkhuni"><p><a class="sc" id="157"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.532" href="#ms.532"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro puriso kulaghare ­hattha­pādac­chinno ñātakehi samparikiṇṇo hoti."
msgstr "On one occasion, a man whose hands and feet had been cut off was in his family’s house, surrounded by his relations."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.2"
msgid "Aññatarā bhikkhunī te manusse etadavoca—"
msgstr "A nun said to those people,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.3"
msgid "“āvuso, icchatha imassa maraṇan”ti?"
msgstr "“Would you like him to die?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.4"
msgid "“Āmāyye, icchāmā”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, Venerable.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.5"
msgid "“Tena hi loṇasovīrakaṃ pāyethā”ti."
msgstr "“Then you should give him salty medicine.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.6"
msgid "Te taṃ loṇasovīrakaṃ pāyesuṃ."
msgstr "They gave him salty medicine"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.7"
msgid "So kālamakāsi."
msgstr "and he died."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.8"
msgid "Tassā kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …."
msgstr "The nun became remorseful. …"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.150" href="#bd.1.150"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.9"
msgid "Atha kho sā bhikkhunī bhikkhunīnaṃ etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "She then informed the nuns,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.10"
msgid "Bhikkhuniyo bhikkhūnaṃ etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "who in turn informed the monks,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.11"
msgid "Bhikkhū bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "who then informed the Master."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.12"
msgid "“Āpattiṃ sā, bhikkhave, bhikkhunī āpannā pārājikan”ti."
msgstr "He said, “Monks, that nun has committed an offense entailing expulsion.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:163.13"
msgid "(103)"
msgstr ""

#. </p></div><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="158"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.533" href="#ms.533"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj3:164.1"
msgid "Tatiya­pā­rāji­kaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The third offense entailing expulsion is finished."

